item.title: Dementhium Problem
item.dc:creator: @Ashi Ashi
item.description:
@Ashi wrote:

Everybody posting on this thread has no loveing idea wtf they’re talking about.

You already know where to change the client IP since you mentioned it which is a start. When you’re hosting and playing on the same computer the IP address should be set to 127.0.0.1. On any other computers on the same network the IP’s should be set to the host computers IP (not your routers). I think you can find the computer’s address using cmd>ipconfig and it should be the IPv4 address if you’re on wireless it’ll be something different.

Read full topic
